Package: bio.spatial.transcriptomics.communication.cellchat.r
Type: Skill
Title: Spatial Transcriptomics Cell-Cell Communication Analysis Skill
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: person("Yang", "Guo", email = "guo@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bioinformatics skill for spatial transcriptomics cell-cell communication analysis using SpatialCellChat (CellChat v3). Supports Visium, Visium HD, Xenium, Slide-seq, CosMx, and Stereo-seq technologies with single-cell resolution inference, spatial distance constraints, contact-dependent signaling, hot spot detection, and deconvolution integration.
